          </button>
          <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-5 pt-1 text-sm text-slate leading-relaxed border-t border-hairline-soft/30 bg-surface-soft/10">
            <p>A tuning fork generates a single, stable, and highly accurate reference frequency. It translates physical kinetic energy into a pure acoustic tone and mechanical vibration, which serves as a benchmark for musicians, a diagnostic sensor for medical professionals, and a vibrational healing stimulator for therapists.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
